# Virtual Library

A simple web-based virtual library application where users can browse and search through a collection of books by title or author. This project demonstrates fundamental front-end web development skills using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- **Dynamic Search Functionality**: Instantly filters books as users type in the search box, allowing for quick and efficient browsing.
- **Responsive Design**: The user interface is designed to be accessible and user-friendly across various devices, including desktops, tablets, and mobile phones.
- **Interactive User Experience**: The application provides an interactive experience by dynamically managing and displaying book data.

## Project Structure

```plaintext
virtual-library/
│
├── index.html   # Main HTML file
├── style.css    # CSS for styling the application
└── script.js    # JavaScript to handle the dynamic functionality
